    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine, showroom condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, a masterpiece of engineering equipped with individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system for optimized valve timing across the rev range. The mechanical synchronicity is flawless, paired with a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory-spec GKN limited-slip differential. The chassis remains structurally impeccable with zero subframe fatigue, and the suspension geometry retains its original precision. Every body panel carries matching VIN tags with original factory paint depth. Inside, the Nappa leather bolsters show no signs of compression or wear. A mechanically transparent vehicle with comprehensive service records, including recent valve adjustments and rod bearing prophylaxis.",
      "price": 47500.0,
